    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058893_4_23615-23643",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "23615-23643",
      "markText": "王婆半日的痛苦没有代价了！王婆一生的痛苦也都是没有代价。",
      "totalCount": 2835,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=23615&rangeEnd=23643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=23615&rangeEnd=23643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058893_3_1166-1243",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1166-1243",
      "markText": "现在是一九三五年十一月十四日的夜里，我在灯下再看完了《生死场》，周围像死一般寂静，听惯的邻人的谈话声没有了，食物的叫卖声也没有了，不过偶有远远的几声犬吠。",
      "totalCount": 2783,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1166&rangeEnd=1243",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1166&rangeEnd=1243"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058893_4_41375-41394",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "41375-41394",
      "markText": "在乡村，人和动物一起忙着生，忙着死……",
      "totalCount": 2090,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=41375&rangeEnd=41394",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=41375&rangeEnd=41394"
    },
    {
