      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4473-4527",
      "markText": "她都是像一摊蜡消融下来。她的性情不好反抗，不好争斗。她的心像永远贮藏着悲哀似的，她的心永远像一块衰弱的白棉。",
      "totalCount": 1792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4473&rangeEnd=4527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4473&rangeEnd=4527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058893_3_1392-1437",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1392-1437",
      "markText": "不过与其听我还在安坐中的牢骚话，不如快看下面的《生死场》，她才会给你们以坚强和挣扎的力气。",
      "totalCount": 1770,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1437",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1437"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058893_4_17773-17831",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "17773-17831",
      "markText": "母亲一向是这样，很爱护女儿，可是当女儿败坏了菜棵，母亲便去爱护菜棵了。农家无论是菜棵，或是一株茅草也要超过人的价值。",
      "totalCount": 1764,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17773&rangeEnd=17831",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ae6328b0813ab7d81g013c18?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17773&rangeEnd=17831"
    },
